snippet.textDisplay: I stopped playing this game in like 2007, but no game's music since can seriously gives me such pleasant flashback memories. Literally every song from this game takes you back years, and I don't want to be one of those guys that lists all these deep feelings they get but the music in this game just takes me back to a time when I didn't have any responsibilities and I could chill online with my friends in RO and there wasn't a care in the world beyond getting to that next job level.
